{"tid":643723,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好迷惘 覺得自己就黎精神分裂","createTime":"2018-04-26T16:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T17:22:37.000Z","uid":135278,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fa90ff587bb17f10e5ea342e50ec6c5884c9588d","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"其實都已經屈左係個心度好長時間<br />\n硬係覺得身邊既人有一部分都有d問題<br />\n中意臨時放飛機<br />\n中意講大話（一次又一次比人踢爆都要搵藉口嗰隻）<br />\n雙面人（同你講到好撚憎佢咁 結果自己痴返落人地度嘻嘻哈哈）<br />\n<br />\n仲有更多我完全解釋唔到既行為 <br />\n例如我好心好意送比佢既野 <br />\n佢係我面前毫不避忌咁拎出去賣比人<br />\n<br />\n例如我有時手頭上有好多野 拎唔曬 袋都裝唔落<br />\n問佢可唔可以幫我拎住先／用佢個袋裝住先<br />\n佢竟然話要收錢<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎由細到大我屋企人都唔會教我咁樣做人<br />\n明明知道有啲行為係唔岩既<br />\n所以我會話我唔中意 同佢地坦白講 呢D行為好令人反感<br />\n然後佢地就會覺得 點解我會連少少野都睇唔順眼<br />\n係我既問題 係我份人太挑剔 係我難相處<br />\n然後佢地就會繼續圍威喂<br />\n跟住我就好似做錯事咁 比人排擠左出黎<br />\n我知身邊有好多錫我既人 佢地會同我講係佢地有問題<br />\n但我真係好迷惘 個人好混亂 到底點解咁委屈仲要比人排？<br />\n點解 點解呢個世界上可以有堆咁樣既人存在？<br />\n我要點做？ 應該點做？以後唔同佢地來往 定 繼續容忍？<br />\n我就黎精神分裂 到底係佢地有問題 定還是真係我錯？<br />\n我覺得我開始分唔到對與錯 每一日都好辛苦<br />\n點算  求屌醒 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a1ce9b9f0c36c1ecccbcf89e76d62d5780b165","tid":643723,"uid":4217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"離開佢地"},{"pid":"f14360c463eb48bac188a30a6594ae2a74b52bc8","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離開佢地</blockquote><br />\n早排覺得對住佢地真係好辛苦<br />\n佢地帶比我太多唔好既回憶<br />\n我呢排甚至因為咁樣而諗過離開香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我唔知咁樣值唔值得"},{"pid":"626794a28c66e30a03a7f079a6e1af6d80fb66cb","tid":643723,"uid":4217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>離開佢地</blockquote><br />\n早排覺得對住佢地真係好辛苦<br />\n佢地帶比我太多唔好既回憶<br />\n我呢排甚至因為咁樣而諗過離開香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我唔知咁樣值唔值得</blockquote><br />\n咁點解唔索性離開 寧願自己一個都唔會再痴返埋佢地到"},{"pid":"eeb3ce8b46b7969f2bb55f36b29db01e0be26ba7","tid":643723,"uid":167301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"絲打<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身邊嘅人成日激嬲我<br />\n激嬲我嘅野有好多eg唔識尊重人同體諒人etc<br />\n但我成日諗究竟係咪我太高要求<br />\n好辛苦成日傷心成日嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3519aa7d671026bae318a669a2b62fd16a9c07fe","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身邊嘅人成日激嬲我<br />\n激嬲我嘅野有好多eg唔識尊重人同體諒人etc<br />\n但我成日諗究竟係咪我太高要求<br />\n好辛苦成日傷心成日嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點講呢<br />\n其實佢地真係經常性做呢啲行為 hurt到自己<br />\n但你又唔可以出聲<br />\n因為你一出聲佢覺得係你要求太嚴<br />\n唔知你有無咁既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39997f6175a91e9ae0d1930898dc3204d99ea737","tid":643723,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"遇人不淑"},{"pid":"dff91dc671b14e87bbf3a89582139d1c7c5ad41c","tid":643723,"uid":167301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3519aa7d671026bae318a669a2b62fd16a9c07fe","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身邊嘅人成日激嬲我<br />\n激嬲我嘅野有好多eg唔識尊重人同體諒人etc<br />\n但我成日諗究竟係咪我太高要求<br />\n好辛苦成日傷心成日嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點講呢<br />\n其實佢地真係經常性做呢啲行為 hurt到自己<br />\n但你又唔可以出聲<br />\n因為你一出聲佢覺得係你要求太嚴<br />\n唔知你有無咁既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T23:48:35.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n所以成日問自己最親嘅人<br />\n自己係咪係啲事上太計較太小器太高要求"},{"pid":"581924660c6ef32f0af5ae6b49b76ff72b1f0451","tid":643723,"uid":47671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T23:52:30.000Z","msg":"講收錢係咪純粹講吓笑渣？<br />\n<br />\n不過你送比佢嘅野係你面前當場賣咗佢呢個幾癲，講吓你曾經送過啲咩比人？"},{"pid":"1674f69c5e38e71398f5c90f3f9e353bf5bcc251","tid":643723,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T23:53:59.000Z","msg":"朋友？家人？"},{"pid":"65797d193cb664a2783a0f10b9f9e77f823d0f37","tid":643723,"uid":107843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T23:57:26.000Z","msg":"劉建明呢個係你最後機會 好好把握"},{"pid":"d64e05da3ed8530c83252a0c50f9cb9a971d3e41","tid":643723,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T00:01:00.000Z","msg":"世界咁大 識過其他人啦<br />\n參加 d 活動啦"},{"pid":"6201182013bbb7d995d6953aed719ce17bfb406d","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身邊嘅人成日激嬲我<br />\n激嬲我嘅野有好多eg唔識尊重人同體諒人etc<br />\n但我成日諗究竟係咪我太高要求<br />\n好辛苦成日傷心成日嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點講呢<br />\n其實佢地真係經常性做呢啲行為 hurt到自己<br />\n但你又唔可以出聲<br />\n因為你一出聲佢覺得係你要求太嚴<br />\n唔知你有無咁既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>有<br />\n所以成日問自己最親嘅人<br />\n自己係咪係啲事上太計較太小器太高要求</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地一定會話係對方唔岩 <br />\n但當你自己一個人既時候又會懷疑自己<br />\n因為三人成虎既道理<br />\n個個都話自己太計較自己就會當真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7ab3decfc00d66278e233d674baacfc3a25ba6","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講收錢係咪純粹講吓笑渣？<br />\n<br />\n不過你送比佢嘅野係你面前當場賣咗佢呢個幾癲，講吓你曾經送過啲咩比人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真架 我個日拎住一盒mask<br />\n無記錯好似$100左右<br />\n佢幫我袋左 好認真咁同我講 收我$50 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送野係送書 朋友話想睇書 <br />\n因為我好中意文學 所以佢問我有無推介<br />\n我有幾本覺得唔錯既書 送左比佢<br />\n可能佢唔岩睇掛<br />\n轉過頭拎上社交平台賣左 比我見到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870aca85b9e5719f12c24689616bfdf16a3c6c80","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友？家人？</blockquote><br />\n朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人對我好好<br />\n由細到大教我唔好怕蝕底 <br />\n適當時要大方少少<br />\n唔好講大話 呢啲觀念<br />\n結果依家識既朋友全部都係相反 搞到我好矛盾<br />\n到底邊樣先係真 <br />\n做人要現實啲自私啲？定還是老實啲 抵諗啲<br />\n對人要誠實直率？ 定係要假少少 圓滑啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa1c3600da9b17903d9212ab247ef24b4bae820","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劉建明呢個係你最後機會 好好把握</blockquote><br />\n邊位劉建明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1871ba53f500a91507c18a64f6a0ca03255517","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世界咁大 識過其他人啦<br />\n參加 d 活動啦</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打建議 <br />\n我都覺呢個係一個好既解決方法<br />\n可以快啲比我脫離現有圈子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fc7a0b0fa1e899fe6ff4e437c4c7032b53e70f","tid":643723,"uid":47671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb7ab3decfc00d66278e233d674baacfc3a25ba6","tid":643723,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講收錢係咪純粹講吓笑渣？<br />\n<br />\n不過你送比佢嘅野係你面前當場賣咗佢呢個幾癲，講吓你曾經送過啲咩比人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真架 我個日拎住一盒mask<br />\n無記錯